title: Benghazi panel head says staffer never mentioned Clinton when fired
text: WASHINGTON (Reuters) - A former investigator for the Republican-led U.S. House committee on Benghazi - who accused it of targeting Hillary Clinton - never expressed unhappiness about Clinton's treatment in discussions leading up to his firing, the panel's head said on Sunday.
